Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.99,0:01:02.25,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,一次次点燃时代的引信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.41,0:01:04.58,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,yeah boom 着火 no matter what you are
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.66,0:01:07.67,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,照天烧 burn the fire just set on the 火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.00,0:01:11.55,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,荒唐无稽的上进心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.63,0:01:13.42,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,空中漂浮 现在Time to time
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.59,0:01:15.76,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,一心不乱加坚忍不拔 alright
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.01,0:01:17.68,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.84,0:01:19.68,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,不是孤身一人 let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.72,0:01:22.97,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,不要停下 来创造未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.35,0:01:30.36,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,如夜里的花一般 无人欣赏也绽放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.07,0:01:36.86,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,从过去继承的flame 在胸口沉睡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.03,0:01:37.82,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,感受它
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.95,0:01:41.37,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,We'are going higher 强烈的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.49,0:01:47.75,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,一次次点燃时代的引信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.87,0:01:51.84,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,将粉碎的命运收回手中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.92,0:01:55.88,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,紧密连结的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.05,0:02:00.85,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,化为无形的光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.01,0:02:04.10,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,化为灰烬意志依然不断绝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.56,0:02:09.85,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,金黄的flame
